6.32.1 libgnunetgns
-------------------

The GNS API itself is extremely simple.  Clients first connec to the GNS
service using ‘GNUNET_GNS_connect’.  They can then perform lookups using
‘GNUNET_GNS_lookup’ or cancel pending lookups using
‘GNUNET_GNS_lookup_cancel’.  Once finished, clients disconnect using
‘GNUNET_GNS_disconnect’.

