6.36 REGEX Subsystem
====================

Using the REGEX subsystem, you can discover peers that offer a
particular service using regular expressions.  The peers that offer a
service specify it using a regular expressions.  Peers that want to
patronize a service search using a string.  The REGEX subsystem will
then use the DHT to return a set of matching offerers to the patrons.

   For the technical details, we have Max’s defense talk and Max’s
Master’s thesis.

* Menu:

